data.description: This beautiful 3 Bedroom, 2.5 Bath home in PRISTINE condition! The extras and bonuses on this home will take your breath away - precious front porch, fully fenced back yard, huge walk in attic and a large garage ready for whatever you have to store! The property line extends past the driveway to the left for additional space and expansion possibilities. The carpet inside has been replaced and is less than two years old. There are split A/C units to keep you cool through these Alabama summers and the unit downstairs was replaced last year! The lovely neighborhood has a lake with walking paths for those days when you want to unwind or get some light exercise. Showings start May 6th- don’t miss your opportunity to own this fabulous home and live in this beautiful neighborhood!
